data.description: PRICE REDUCTION PLUS $4000 CREDIT TOWARDS BUYER'S CLOSING COSTS!!! AMAZING OPPORTUNITY FOR THIS 4 BEDROOM HOME, USDA, VA AND FHA QUALIFIED! Nearly New! Light and Bright this Impeccable 4-bedroom 2 bath home is move-in ready! Located in a quiet and charming community, Built in 2020, this modern gem showcases elegant laminate wood flooring throughout, carpet in bedrooms, quartz countertops in the kitchen and bathrooms, ceiling fans in every bedroom and the living room, and welcoming recessed lighting. The house and garage have recently been painted, the garage boasts epoxy flooring, and new carpets ensure comfort underfoot. Beyond the home's impressive features, its location is unbeatable, just minutes from Interstate 4, Route 27, Posner Park shopping mall, Champions Gate, and Disney theme parks. Plus, there are dining and shopping options galore. In this community, you'll also have access to a pool, playground, and walking trails, making this property perfect for both relaxation and outdoor enthusiasts. This is your oasis! schedule a viewing today and step into the life you've been dreaming of!
